FiscalYear
==========

Add 'fiscal_year' method, that returns the fiscal year, to Ruby Date, Time and DateTime classes.


Example
=======

% script/console
Loading development environment (Rails 2.2.2)
>> Date.new(2009, 3, 31).fiscal_year
=> 2008
>> Date.new(2009, 4, 1).fiscal_year
=> 2009

